name: Immortality Cultivation: I can use my clansmen’s energy and blood to add points
summary: Travel through a time of chaos and chaos, where demons are rampant.At the beginning, the ancestor of the Luo family was about to expire and half of his body was buried in the ground.Are you about to die just after traveling through time?What kind of human suffering is this?Just when Luo Changfeng was a little confused and a little desperate.He discovered that he could actually consume more energy and blood from the Luo family members.With smaller hands, your lifespan increases.With smaller hands, your cultivation level will soar.With small hands, the technique will be perfect....Therefore, Luo Changfeng embarked on the path of strengthening the family and constantly adding points.
